{"tid":2304860,"cid":26,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人識java可以幫幫我?","createTime":"2020-11-29T07:11:53.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-13T13:57:43.000Z","uid":385977,"like":0,"dislike":70,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"eb6885443db1d75ddedf0fec42b1985ac20cd123","tid":2304860,"uid":385977,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-29T07:11:53.000Z","msg":"我想做一個自動出數學題的java，應該如何令他自動出題和編寫答題者可以設置問題數並在回答後顯示記錄正確答案的數量?<br />\n如下圖<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sorXx5A.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsorXx5A.png&h=f9ad84bb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<pre><code data-type=\"\">\n    import java.util.Scanner;\n     \n    public class Main {\n     \n    public static void main(String[] args){\n        System.out.println(&quot;Welcome to the IP Math Quiz&quot;+&quot;\\n ***Main Menu***&quot;+&quot;\\n1) Remaining&quot;+&quot;\\n2) Greatest Common Divisor (GCD)&quot;+&quot;\\n3) Least Common Multiple ( LCM) &quot;+&quot; \\n4) division &quot;+&quot; \\n5) plural &quot;+&quot; \\n9) exit &quot;);\n     int num1, num2;\n  num1 = (int)(Math.random() *100) + 1;\n  num2 = (int)(Math.random() *100) + 1;\n  System.out.println(maxCommonDivisor(num1, num2));// 调用maxCommonDivisor()方法\n  System.out.println(minCommonMultiple(num1, num2));// 调用minCommonMultiple()方法\n\n }\n \n // 递归法求最大公约数\n public static int maxCommonDivisor(int m, int n) {\n  if (m &lt; n) {// 保证m&gt;n,若m&lt;n,则进行数据交换\n   int temp = m;\n   m = n;\n   n = temp;\n  }\n  if (m % n == 0) {// 若余数为0,返回最大公约数\n   return n;\n  } else { // 否则,进行递归,把n赋给m,把余数赋给n\n   return maxCommonDivisor(n, m % n);\n  }\n }\n // 求最小公倍数\n public static int minCommonMultiple(int m, int n) {\n  return m * n / maxCommonDivisor(m, n);\n }\n}\n  </code></pre>"},{"pid":"f834810829e1fe1e9b3e86f5bd209e5e1b6e03de","tid":2304860,"uid":46587,"like":55,"dislike":0,"score":55,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-29T07:14:03.000Z","msg":"支那仔番百度問啦"},{"pid":"453e87ec6e55e97a9d6b10775861ba3bf7b16318","tid":2304860,